text = "PLAYER 1                          PLAYER 2
Move          WASD                   Arrow keys
Gather        E (hold)               . (hold)
Build tower   Q                      ,
Attack        Space                  /
Pause         Esc or Start           Esc or Start
Restart       R                      R

GOAL
Gather Essence from cyan wells. Queue towers on
green pads (25 Essence). Survive 5 surges.
Anyone can do any job — share the bank.

PADS
Switch Pro / Joy-Con: device 0 = P1, device 1 = P2
A gather · B attack · X build · left stick move"
